#: ../../project/validation.rst:91 9429f7857e8247f4be1af60af8011273
msgid "This description of the Sampling Design Tool in ArcGIS: https://www.arcgis.com/home/item.html?id=28f08ca526ae44e8ac107a2a0d5f50e3"
